data.description: Prosper ISD!!!  Fabulous North-South facing ONE-STORY home in coveted Light Farms Sweetwater section! Shows like new! Beautiful modern interior with neutral colors and open floorplan. Kitchen features GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, gas cooktop, stainless steel appliances, white cabinetry, & breakfast bar. PLANTATION SHUTTERS on all windows. Spacious open family room and dining area. Owners retreat has dual sinks, vanity sitting area, & large shower. Two secondary bedrooms plus a STUDY with french doors - makes a great 4th bedroom. All bedrooms & study have WALK-IN CLOSETS. No neighbors behind the house!  Enjoy the neighborhood pool, private fitness center, lake, sports courts, walking trails, and beautiful Constellation Park. HOA takes care of front yard maintenance.
